## Open project decisions

Record only project-level decisions that affect multiple features. Feature-local questions belong in the feature design and Beads review steps.

## Recommended next work

Use the dstack feature resolver through `/plan-features` or `/start-feature` to select the next ready feature epic by
Beads readiness, priority, and feature number. Record the recommended command as `/start-feature <num>-<slug>` and keep
this narrative synchronized during planning and close-out.
